UKUNGCOLA komoya kungaba nomthelela wokuthi abahaqwe yiCovid-19 bagule kakhulu, badinge ukulaliswa ezibhedlela noma bashone. Lokhu kuvezwe wucwaningo olushicilelwe emqingweni wezempilo, iCanadian Medical Association Journal, ngesonto eledlule. Abacwaningi, ababuye babe ngababhali kulo mqingo, bathole ukuthi ukuhlale uhogela umoya ongcolile kunomthelela wokuthi uma uhaqwe yiCovid-19 ugule kakhulu ngenxa yokuthi amaphaphu asuke ebuthaka. USolwazi Chen Chen weNyuvesi iCalifornia San Diego, ongomunye wabhali nomcwaningi kulolu cwaningo olwenziwe ngabantu abangu-8 630 ebebelaliswe ezibhedlela ngenxa yezifo ezihambisana neCovid-19, uthe bebebheka iziguli ezihlala ezindaweni ezaziwayo ukuthi zinezinga eliphezulu lokungcola komoya. Kulaba bantu okwenziwe ngabo ucwaningo bekukhona ebebelaliswe emagumbini abadinga ukunakekelwa okuthe xaxa nabangu-2137 abashonele ezibhedlela bebulawa yiCovid-19. Ukuze kubonakale ukuthi ukhona yini umthelela odalwa ukuphefumula umoya ongcolile, uthe bebebheka ukuthi abahaqwe yiCovid-19 ngabe bake bahogela umoya ongcolile isikhathi eside yini, okungaba phakathi ku-2015 kuya ku-2019, besebenzisa ulwazi olugciniwe khona eCanada. Kutholakale ukuthi abantu abahlala ezindaweni ezaziwayo ukuthi zinomoya ongcolile kunamathuba amaningi okuthi balaliswe ezibhedlela uma kwenzeka behaqwa yilolu bhubhane. Abacwaningi bathole ukuthi umoya, i-03, yiwona oyingozi kakhulu oholela ekutheni uma abantu bengenwe yiCovid-19 bagule kakhulu noma bashone. Abacwaningi bathi ucwaningo lwabo luveza ukuthi kubaluleke kangakanani ukuthi kuhlanzwe umoya nokuthi kube nemigomo elawula ukungcoliswa komoya. "Njengoba ubhubhane lweCovid-19 luqhubeka, lolu cwaningo luveza ukuthi uma bengaba baningi abantu abahogela umoya ongcolile abahaqwa yiCovid-19, kungaba nengcindezi ezikhungweni zezempilo ngoba bangaba baningi abantu abadinga ukulaliswa ezibhedlela," kuxwayisa uSolwazi uChen Chen. 